</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_562" id="280r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, dem <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>Döring<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>Meichs<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Wolfharts
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> zu Leipczk, umb erb und eygen, daz er bey uns
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> sülle etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und haben umb <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den Eckhart Neydunk,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, den die sache antrift, für uns besandt und
                                <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit im
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt. So steet die sache, als sie
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürgebe<ex>n</ex></expan> ist und als es
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurtt</expan> hat, gar ungleich gen
                                <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan>. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        wil <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Wolfhart
                            <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>mittvaste<ex>n</ex></expan> schieristkünstig</q>14.03.1423</note></app>
<add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan></add> zu uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so sol er <pb facs="#facs_563" id="280v"/>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
                        und bey uns für <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> geleyt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; <add>alsdenn</add> wil im der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, Eckhart Neydunk,
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewings
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<add>ungeverlich</add>, des auch wir <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Wolfhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>, ob er <expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns
                                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt,
                            <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> helffen
                            <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>;
                            <add>warczu er denn recht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> sol und mit
                            recht bey uns erlangt, des <expan>gönne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils wol </add>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>circu<ex>m</ex>cisio<ex>n</ex>is</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>. </ab>
</div>
